title: Ground News - Sanjay Dutt's Daughter Reunites With Him In Dubai, Shares Twinning Pictures With Half-Brother
text:
Summary by bollywoodshaadis.com Sanjay Dutt's elder daughter, Trishala Dutt from his first wife, Richa Sharma, likes to stay miles away from Bollywood. However, she is still one of the most-loved star kids in India. Sanjay Dutt's millions of fans eagerly wait for Trishala to post about her life with Sanjay Dutt, who is considered one of the finest actors. Trishala not only shares a cordial bond with her father but with his wife, Maanayata Dutt and their twins Shahraan and Iqra… Share menu More
